## How It All Flows

```
Artist replies to your IG DM
        │
        ▼
Meta servers detect new message
        │
        ▼
POST /api/ig/meta-webhook
        │
        ├── Skip echo (messages YOU sent)
        ├── GET graph.facebook.com/{psid}?fields=username
        │         → resolves PSID to @artisthandle
        ├── Find lead by @instagramHandle in DB
        ├── Log Activity: REPLY_RECEIVED
        ├── Update lead: CONTACTED → FOLLOW_UP
        │
        ▼
triggerIgReplyNotification()
        │
        ▼
Novu "ig-reply-received" workflow
        │
        ▼
🔔 Bell badge in your Sidebar
```

